original_title: Katsakh: The People Want the Fall of the Regime
overview: A capsule from Chantal Partamian’s "Katsakh" project, experiments on and with film originally published on Instagram. “Katsakh” means vinegar in Armenian, in reference to the vinegar syndrome, “the chemical degradation that occurs with cellulous acetate film”.
title: Katsakh: The People Want the Fall of the Regime
